odd
===

odd, the Odoo addon linter

Installation
------------

Install using pip:

.. code-block:: bash

    pip install odd

Usage
-----

.. code-block:: bash

    odd 13 path/to/your/odoo_v13/addon

.. note::
   *odd* does not detect issues out of the box, install `odd-bunch`_ for some plugins
   that do.

.. _odd-bunch: https://pypi.org/project/odd-bunch/

